The IAS is located at Orsay at about 15 km at the south of PARIS.
Access by Metro : line RER B station Orsay
Access by car : N 118 Exit Orsay
The address is :
C.N.R.S.-I.A.S Campus Universitaire d'Orsay - Bat 121
91405 ORSAY Cedex - FRANCE




